PrecisAppointment of D. IAN GLEN, of Ottawa, Ontario, as a full-time member of the National Parole Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a period of five years; and designation of D. IAN GLEN as the Chairperson of the National Parole Board; effective May 22, 2001.
